metadata.name: Keeper of Seeds
metadata.description:
Inspired by The Keeper of Seeds in Mad Max: Fury Road. She was a mother who preserved the last flower and plant seeds from Vulvalini in a post-apocalyptical world.

This world looks a little different, driven by digitization and space-based energies. But the Keeper's goal remains the same: preserve and nurture seeds of nature's flora. 

1640 x 2360
